<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>NGO Connect</title>
  <link
    rel="stylesheet"
    href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/5.0.0-alpha1/css/bootstrap.min.css"
    integrity="sha384-r4NyP46KrjDleawBgD5tp8Y7UzmLA05oM1iAEQ17CSuDqnUK2+k9luXQOfXJCJ4I"
    crossorigin="anonymous"
  />
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: url('/images/home.jpg') no-repeat center center fixed;
      background-size: cover;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    }

    /* White overlay for readability */
    body::before {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      height: 100%;
      width: 100%;
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4); /* Lightens image */
      z-index: -1;
    }

    .cover-container {
      background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); /* semi-transparent black */
      backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
      color: white;
      padding: 3rem;
      border-radius: 15px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
      text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px black;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    p.lead {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 1rem auto;
    }

    .btn-custom {
      background-color: #17a2b8;
      color: white;
      font-weight: bold;
      border: none;
      padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      transition: background 0.3s ease;
    }

    .btn-custom:hover {
      background-color: #138496;
    }

    .nav-link {
      color: #fff !important;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .nav-link:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body class="d-flex text-center">
  <div class="cover-container d-flex w-100 h-100 p-3 mx-auto flex-column justify-content-center align-items-center">
    <header class="mb-auto w-100">
      <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center px-4">
        <h3 class="mb-0">NGO Connect</h3>
        <nav class="nav nav-masthead justify-content-end">
          <a class="nav-link active" href="/">Home</a>
          <a class="nav-link" href="/ngos">Explore NGOs</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="text-center px-3">
      <h1>Support NGOs, Change Lives</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        NGO Connect is a platform designed to bridge the gap between passionate individuals and impactful non-profit organizations. Users can explore a wide range of verified NGOs working across causes like education, healthcare, environmental conservation, and rural development. Each NGO profile highlights its mission, current needs, and ways people can contributeâ€”be it through donations, volunteering, or spreading awareness. Whether you're looking to make a difference or support a cause close to your heart, NGO Connect makes it easy to take meaningful action.
      </p>
      <a href="/ngos" class="btn btn-lg btn-custom">View NGOs</a>
    </main>

    <footer class="mt-auto text-white-50">
      <p>&copy; 2025 NGO Connect</p>
    </footer>
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
    integrity="sha384-pjaaA8dDz/FSYpOJb0aG+JyZr6fxo8HcFrll9H57N7/QpPjj+3F4AvhEBXvF5Szj"
    crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>
